</section>

<!--Lead the Way Alt Section Start-->
<section class="about-three lead-the-way-alt-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__left">
                    <div class="section-title text-left">
                        <span class="section-title__tagline editable">Community Foundation of Teton Valley</span>
                        <h2 class="section-title__title editable">Lead the Way as a Tin Cup Challenger</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">Tin Cup works because generosity multiplies. Donors support the nonprofits they love. Challengers amplify those gifts, strengthening Teton Valley's nonprofit community and increasing total impact. As a Challenger, you provide leadership-level support that makes the match possible and inspires others to give.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__right">
                    <div class="about-three__img-box wow slideInRight" data-wow-delay="100ms" data-wow-duration="2500ms">
                        <div class="about-three__img">
                            <img src="/assets/images/tin-cup/nonprofit-parade.jpg" alt="Tin Cup Challenge Community" class="editable" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="about-three__border"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!--Lead the Way Alt Section End-->

<!--How the Match Works + Join the Match Combined Section Start-->
<section class="how-match-works-section" style="padding: 80px 0; background: var(--cftv-navy);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-stretch">
            <div class="col-xl-6 mb-4 mb-xl-0">
                <div class="about-three__left" style="margin-top: 0;">
                    <div class="section-title text-left">
                        <h2 class="section-title__title editable" style="color: #fff;">How the Match Works</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable" style="color: #fff;">Challengers contribute to a pooled Match Fund that partially matches designated gifts during the Giving Period. Instead of supporting just one nonprofit, your gift benefits all participating nonprofits.</p>
                    <div style="margin-left: 30px;">
                        <h3 class="editable" style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 24px; color: #fff; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">A Strong Match</h3>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled about-three__bullet-list">
                            <li class="editable"><span class="bullet-icon"><i class="fa fa-circle"></i></span>Raises more total dollars</li>
                            <li class="editable"><span class="bullet-icon"><i class="fa fa-circle"></i></span>Inspires broader participation</li>
                            <li class="editable"><span class="bullet-icon"><i class="fa fa-circle"></i></span>Supports nonprofits of every size</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__right" style="margin-top: 0;">
                    <div class="about-three__img-box" style="overflow: visible;">
                        <div style="background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 50px 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: left;">
                            <h2 style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 38px; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin-bottom: 25px;" class="editable">Join the Match</h2>
                            <p class="editable" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin-bottom: 30px;">Gifts of any size are welcome. Leadership and multi-year commitments help build a strong, reliable match each year. When you give as a Challenger, you're not directing dollars — you're increasing what's possible.</p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="#" class="thm-btn gold-navy__btn">Become a Tin Cup Challenger</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
